'''Adrienne Ako Anomgbo Koutouan''' (wavutse 1969)  numukinnyi wa filimi na comedi muri  Cote d'Ivoire<ref>https://www.afrikmag.com/adrienne-koutouan-la-comedienne-vient-en-aide-aux-femmes-du-village-dabobote/</ref>.

== Ubuzima ==
Koutouan ni umwe mu baturage ba Tchaman kandi yavukiye mu mudugudu wa Abobo-Té muri komine ya Abobo hafi ya Abidjan <ref>https://emirate.wiki/wiki/Adrienne_Koutouan</ref>.  Yifuzaga kuba umukinnyi wa filimi kuva akiri umwana, nubwo iki gitekerezo kitakiriwe neza n'ababyeyi be<ref>http://africultures.com/personnes/?no=7718</ref>. Yatangiye umwuga we mu myaka ya za 1980 mu itsinda ry’ikinamico "Fétiche éburnéen".  Mu 1986, Koutouan yagizwe umubyinnyi mwiza muri ballet ya Coryte d'Ivoire.<ref>https://artsandculture.google.com/entity/g121vr3f_?hl=nl</ref> 

Koutouan yahawe ibihembo byinshi, harimo kwitwara neza mu bagore mu iserukiramuco rya Namur mu Bubiligi mu 1998, kwitwara neza mu bagore mu iserukiramuco rya M-Net ryabereye i Johannesburg mu 1999, ndetse n’umukinnyi  wa [[Afurika]] witwaye neza mu iserukiramuco rya Pabbah muri [[Nijeriya]] mu 2002.<ref>https://www.bbc.com/afrique/47769140</ref>  Mu mwaka wa 2006, Koutouan yahawe igihembo cya Gold Standard mu iserukiramuco rya Filime na Televiziyo bya Panafrican rya Ouagadougou kubera kwitwara neza mu rukurikirane rwa ''Quand les éléphants se battent'' <ref>https://www.allocine.fr/personne/fichepersonne_gen_cpersonne=27092.html</ref>. Azwi cyane muri Coryte [[Kote Divuwari|d'Ivoire]] kubera uruhare rwe nka Rosalie mu rukurikirane rwa ''Faut pas fâcher'' .  Muri 2008, Koutouan yakinnye nka Infirmière Antoinette muri Dr. Boris ari kumwe na Ahmed Souaney<ref>https://www.ivoiresoir.net/mort-de-angeline-nadie-adrienne-koutouan-se-prononce/</ref>. 

Ku ya 14 Mata 2019, Koutouan yahawe icyubahiro mu birori byo kwizihiza imyaka 30 amaze ari umukinnyi wa filime, ahabwa itandukaniro riturutse kuri guverinoma.<ref>https://en.unifrance.org/directories/person/141832/adrienne-koutouan</ref> Yageze ku ntera ya ofisiye mu cyubahiro cy’umuco, na Minisiteri y’umuco na Francophonie. Umugatolika wubahaga Imana, Koutouan na we yagize misa mu cyubahiro cye.<ref>http://www.africine.org/personne/adrienne-koutouan/7718</ref> 

